        <li>The first word should stay lowercase; use <code class="text-stone-900 bg-stone-200/70 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-xs">capitalize()</code> on all subsequent words to uppercase only their first letter.</li>
        <li>You can build the result by joining a list of transformed words: <code class="text-stone-900 bg-stone-200/70 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-xs">"".join(words)</code>.</li>
